@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home page";
}

<html>
<head>
  <title>Elderly Care Management</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 100px auto;
      padding: 40px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
    }
    
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    ul {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    
    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .img-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    
    .img-container img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-center">Elderly Care Management</h1>
    <p class="lead">Elderly Care Management is an innovative mobile and web application designed to assist individuals in managing the healthcare and well-being of their elderly loved ones. It aims to provide a comprehensive solution for organizing and monitoring the various aspects of eldercare, ensuring a higher quality of life for seniors and peace of mind for their families.</p>
    
    <h2 class="mb-4">Key Features:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Profile Management: Users can create profiles for their elderly loved ones, including basic personal information, medical history, allergies, and emergency contacts.</li>
      <li>Medication Tracking: The app allows users to schedule and track medication intake for their elderly family members. It sends reminders and notifications to ensure medications are taken on time.</li>
      <li>Health Monitoring: Users can record and track vital signs such as blood pressure, heart rate, and glucose levels. This feature enables early detection of any health issues and helps maintain a health history.</li>
      <li>Appointment Management: The app includes a calendar system to schedule and manage medical appointments, including doctor visits, therapy sessions, and other healthcare-related events.</li>
      <li>Caregiver Coordination: Users can invite and collaborate with caregivers, enabling effective communication and coordination of caregiving tasks. Caregivers can access relevant information and provide real-time updates.</li>
      <li>Emergency Alerts: In case of emergencies, the app allows users to trigger alerts to designated contacts, providing them with important information and the ability to respond quickly.</li>
      <li>Reminders and Notifications: The app sends reminders for medication, appointments, and other important events to both the elderly individual and the caregiver, ensuring nothing is overlooked.</li>
      <li>Communication and Messaging: The app includes a messaging feature to facilitate seamless communication between family members, caregivers, and healthcare professionals involved in the elderly person's care.</li>
      <li>Resources and Information: The app provides access to a library of resources, articles, and information related to eldercare, including tips for healthy aging, caregiving advice, and community support services.</li>
      <li>Data Security and Privacy: The app prioritizes the security and privacy of user data, employing robust encryption techniques and adhering to strict privacy policies to safeguard sensitive information.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="img-container">
      <img src="path/to/your/image.jpg" alt="Elderly Care Image" class="img-fluid" />
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
